snippet.title: 25games
snippet.description:
25games was founded in 2016 by two friends: Severin & Simon. 
Our first goal was to publish a action-adventure game called Kordex. Sadly we wasn't able to find enough support to continue development. Severin left the video tutorial production. So just Simon is left.
However, the Youtube channel was growing nicely. So I decided to continue producing videos for you!
